```json
{
  "application": "trimmomatic",
  "other_software": [
    "cutadapt",
    "sed"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": {
    "nodes": 1,
    "ppn": 1,
    "walltime": "10:00:00",
    "pmem": "5gb",
    "queue": "bio"
  },
  "modules": [
    "trimmomatic"
  ],
  "libraries": [
    "trimmomatic.jar"
  ],
  "input_files": [
    "dros_biorep_list.csv",
    "{LINE}_{MV}_{REP}_{LANE1}_adapter_trimmed_run_2_5_prime.fq",
    "{LINE}_{MV}_{REP}_{LANE2}_adapter_trimmed_run_2_5_prime.fq"
  ],
  "output_files": [
    "{LINE}_{MV}_{REP}_{LANE1}_${LANE2}_Drosophila_trimmomatic_run2_5_prime.log",
    "{LINE}_{MV}_{REP}_{LANE1}_trimmomatic_run_2_5_prime_paired.fq",
    "{LINE}_{MV}_{REP}_{LANE1}_trimmomatic_run_2_5_prime_unpaired.fq",
    "{LINE}_{MV}_{REP}_{LANE2}_trimmomatic_run_2_5_prime_paired.fq",
    "{LINE}_{MV}_{REP}_{LANE2}_trimmomatic_run_2_5_prime_unpaired.fq"
  ],
  "command": "java -classpath $HPC_TRIMMOMATIC_LIB/trimmomatic.jar org.usadellab.trimmomatic.TrimmomaticPE -phred64 -threads 3 -trimlog $TRIMOLOG $READS1 $READS2 $TRIM1 $TRIM2 $TRIM3 $TRIM4 HEADCROP:10 LEADING:3 TRAILING:3 SLIDINGWINDOW:4:15 MINLEN:60"
}
```
